# Keep LF line endings for files executed inside Linux containers, so a commit
# from Windows doesn't break the image (e.g. entrypoint.sh with CRLF → bad
# interpreter). Other text files are normalized to LF in the repo too.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile* text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
